dc_title_s: A new map of London and its environs, 1830.
dc_description_s: Accompanied by index: consulting index to Cook's new plan of London, Westminster, and the borough of Southwark, with improvements to the present time. 1 map: dissected and mounted on canvas; 41 x 75 cm., folded in cover 16 cm.  1 booklet (6 leaves; 14 cm) This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
